---
// src/pages/blog/types-of-business-websites.astro
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Types of Business Websites: Which One Do You Need? — 404found.studio"
  description="Landing pages, brochure sites, e-commerce, web apps — learn which type of website is right for your Malaysian business."
>
  <Navbar />
  <article class="article">
    <div class="article-header">
      <p class="tag">Strategy</p>
      <h1>Types of Business Websites:<br /><span>Which One Do You Need?</span></h1>
      <p class="meta">4 min read · 404found.studio</p>
    </div>

    <div class="article-body">
      <p>Not every business needs the same kind of website. Choosing the wrong type wastes money and slows your growth. Here's a clear breakdown of the main types of business websites and exactly when to use each one.</p>

      <h2>1. Landing Page</h2>
      <p>A single, focused page with one goal: convert visitors into leads or customers. No navigation menu to distract. Just a compelling headline, your value proposition, and a call to action.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Product launches, ad campaigns, freelancers, service businesses, event registrations.</p>
      <p><strong>Cost:</strong> RM800 – RM1,500 &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Timeline:</strong> 3–5 days</p>

      <div class="callout">
        <strong>When to choose a landing page:</strong> You're running Google or Meta ads and need a dedicated page that matches your ad copy. Or you offer one core service and want to keep visitors focused.
      </div>

      <h2>2. Brochure / Business Website</h2>
      <p>A multi-page website that tells your full story — who you are, what you offer, your team, your work, and how to contact you. The digital equivalent of a professional brochure.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> SMEs, professional services (law, accounting, consulting), clinics, contractors, agencies.</p>
      <p><strong>Cost:</strong> RM1,500 – RM3,500 &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Timeline:</strong> 1–2 weeks</p>

      <h2>3. E-commerce Website</h2>
      <p>A full online store where customers can browse products, add to cart, and pay — all without leaving your site. Includes inventory management, order tracking, and payment gateway integration.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Retail businesses, F&amp;B, fashion, electronics, and any business selling physical or digital products.</p>
      <p><strong>Cost:</strong> RM3,000 – RM8,000 &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Timeline:</strong> 2–4 weeks</p>

      <h2>4. Booking / Appointment System</h2>
      <p>Lets customers schedule appointments, classes, or services directly from your website — with automated confirmations and reminders sent via email or WhatsApp.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Salons, clinics, tutors, fitness studios, car workshops, photographers.</p>
      <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Business website + RM500 add-on &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Timeline:</strong> 2 weeks</p>

      <h2>5. Custom Web Application</h2>
      <p>A purpose-built system that goes beyond a standard website — member portals, staff dashboards, custom CRMs, inventory systems, or multi-vendor marketplaces. Requires a full scoping discussion.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Businesses with unique operational needs that off-the-shelf tools can't solve.</p>
      <p><strong>Cost:</strong> Quote required &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong>Timeline:</strong> 4–8 weeks</p>

      <h2>How to Choose</h2>
      <p>Ask yourself these questions:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Do you sell products online? → E-commerce</li>
        <li>Do you take appointments? → Business website + booking add-on</li>
        <li>Are you running a specific campaign or promoting one service? → Landing page</li>
        <li>Do you want to establish your brand and explain your services? → Business website</li>
        <li>Do you have a workflow that existing tools can't handle? → Custom system</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Still not sure? Use our AI consultant to describe your situation and we'll recommend the right approach for your budget and goals.</p>
      <a href="/" class="cta-link">Chat with AI Consultant →</a>
    </div>
  </article>
  <Footer />
</Base>

